high_descs: Turn around, then turn left past the island and locate the microwave.
Open the microwave and take out the cup. Shut the door.
Carry the cup and turn around, and right past the island. Turn left to face the sink.
Place the cup in the sink and turn on the water. Turn off the water and pick up the cup, full of water.
Carry the cup and turn to the the left and then left again around the island. Move to the microwave.
Open the microwave and place the cup inside. Shut the door.
anns.task_desc: Fill a cup with water and place in the microwave.

high_descs: Turn left, move to the microwave on the counter.
Take the black cup out of the microwave.
Turn around, move to the door, turn right, move to the sink, across the room to the left.
Put the cup in the sink, fill the cup with water.
Turn around, bring the filled cup back to the microwave across the room to the left.
Put the filled cup in the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Put a filled cup of water in the microwave.

high_descs: Turn around and go to the microwave.
Open the microwave and pick up the cup and close it.
Turn back around and head to the sink.
Put the cup in the sink and fill it with water then remove it..
Turn around and go back to the microwave.
Place the cup back in side the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Take a cup from the microwave and fill with water, place it back in the microwave.
